redmine2abraflexi for Debian
----------------------------

This package installs the Redmine to AbraFlexi invoice generator.
It integrates with AbraFlexi and Redmine to export workhours into invoices.

To use the tool, configure the connection in `.env` or pass the settings
via environment variables, and run `redmine2abraflexi-invoice`.

